Author: norwegian_twat
Text: diagnosed with atypical bulimia here  guess just means i alternate between restricting/binging/binging and purging, but hover mostly over binging and purging? idk feels like ednos but not quite  and as other comment mentioned id say is kinda accurate. been binging and purging most days of february, but sometimes bp and then binge more but dont purge etcetc so its like ukno. most ive purged in a day is like 4 times too so not rly too serious, and some days i dont purge at all, despite eating/binging. but last month i spent nearly every day without food so its a rollercoaster for sure

Author: algorthin
Text: The most common reason Ive seen that someone is diagnosed w atypical bulimia is that they don't bp often enough but all atypical bulimia means is "this eating disorder most closely resembles bulimia but doesn't quite meet every bit of the diagnostic criteria." Doesn't comment on severity.
